    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 8.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第8课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "The Best and the Worst.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "最好的和最差的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why is Joe's garden the most beautiful one in the town?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么乔的花园是镇上最漂亮的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Joe Sanders has the most beautiful garden in our town.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "乔·桑德斯拥有我们镇上最漂亮的花园。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Nearly everybody enters for the nicest garden competition each year.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "每年几乎人人都参加“最佳花园”竞赛。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "But Joe wins every time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "但每次都是乔获胜。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Bill Frith's garden is larger than Joe's.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "比尔·弗里斯的花园比乔的花园大。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Bill works harder than Joe and grows more flowers and vegetables.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "比尔比乔更勤奋，种的花和蔬菜也更多。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "But Joe's garden is more interesting.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "但乔的花园更有情趣。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "He has made neat paths and has built a wooden bridge over a pool.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他修筑了整洁的小径，还在池塘上架了一座木桥。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I like gardens too, but I do not like hard work.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我也喜欢花园，但我不愿意辛勤劳动。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Every year I enter for the garden competition too, and I always win a little prize for the worst garden in the town.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "每年我也参加花园竞赛，而且总能获得镇上最差花园的小奖。"
      }
    }
  ],
